| `-encrypted-boot  253:5    0   512M  0 crypt /boot
`-sda3                8:3    0 464.8G  0 part  
  `-root            253:2    0 464.8G  0 crypt 
    |-notebook-root 253:3    0   100G  0 lvm   /
    `-notebook-home 253:4    0   200G  0 lvm   /home

